====================
Japan country states
====================

This module updates country state data of Japan with translation.

Installation
============

``base_country_state_translatable`` from ``partner-contact`` repository is
needed as a dependency.

Usage
=====

.. image:: https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas
   :alt: Try me on Runbot
   :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/257/11.0

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues
<https://github.com/OCA/l10n-japan/issues>`_. In case of trouble, please
check there if your issue has already been reported. If you spotted it first,
help us smash it by providing detailed and welcomed feedback.
